sequenceDiagram
    participant Trigger as Operator or scheduler
    participant Dream as Dream batch
    participant Lease as dream_runs lease (S5)
    participant Data as Data-access APIs
    participant LLMAdapter as LLM adapter
    participant LLM as LLM service

    Trigger->>Dream: run_dream(reason)
    Dream->>Lease: acquire_or_start()
    alt fresh live run exists
      Lease-->>Dream: live_run(run_id, phase, elapsed, eta)
      Dream-->>Trigger: status_report, TTY exit 0, non-TTY exit non-zero
    else no live row, or stale row closed
      Lease->>Lease: if stale, mark old row timed_out and insert new run row
      Lease-->>Dream: lease_acquired(run_id, deadline_at)
      Note over Dream,Lease: Stale process writes are ignored unless run_id still owns the live row.
      Note over Dream,Lease: Heartbeat task ticks last_heartbeat_at every dream.heartbeat_interval_seconds.
      Dream->>Data: compute_dream_readiness()
      Data-->>Dream: pending_signal_tokens, pending_successful_chains, oldest_pending_at
      alt below readiness thresholds and not forced
        Dream->>Data: delete_stale_signals(prune_window)
        Dream->>Lease: terminate(skipped, pending counts, skip_reason)
        Dream-->>Trigger: dream_exit(skipped)
      else readiness passes or --force
        Dream->>Lease: set_phase(light)
        Dream->>Data: read_recent_signals(window)
        Data-->>Dream: signal_batch
        Dream->>Lease: poll_cancel()
        Lease-->>Dream: not_cancelled
        Dream->>Lease: set_phase(rem)
        Dream->>Data: read_memory_context(bounds)
        Data-->>Dream: memory_context
        Dream->>Lease: poll_cancel()
        Lease-->>Dream: not_cancelled
        Dream->>Lease: set_phase(deep)
        loop deep-phase chunks
          Dream->>Lease: poll_cancel_and_deadline()
          Lease-->>Dream: not_cancelled(remaining_runtime)
          Dream->>LLMAdapter: analyze(chunk, timeout=remaining_runtime)
          LLMAdapter->>LLM: provider_request(messages)
          alt provider returns before deadline
            LLM-->>LLMAdapter: provider_response(findings)
            LLMAdapter-->>Dream: findings
            Dream->>Data: upsert_memories(findings.memories)
            Dream->>Data: enqueue_cli_proposals(findings.forge_briefs)
            Dream->>Data: enqueue_persona_proposals(findings.persona_briefs)
            Dream->>Lease: poll_cancel()
          else deadline expires
            LLMAdapter-->>Dream: timeout
            Dream->>Lease: terminate(timed_out)
            Dream-->>Trigger: dream_exit(timed_out)
          end
          alt cancel observed after completed chunk
            Note over Dream,Data: Persisted-so-far drafts stay and remaining chunks are abandoned.
            Dream->>Lease: terminate(cancelled)
            Dream-->>Trigger: dream_exit(cancelled)
          end
        end
        Dream->>Lease: set_phase(prune)
        Dream->>Data: delete_stale_signals(prune_window)
        Dream->>Lease: terminate(succeeded, phase_durations)
        Note over Lease: phase_durations update the EWMA used by typhoon dream status ETA.
        Dream-->>Trigger: dream_exit(success)
      end
    end
    Note over Dream,Data: Dream proposes new work. Ratification remains outside dream.
